                                                            </p>
                                                            <p>
                                                                Your proposal has been <strong
                                                                >approved</strong> to the ${object.event_id.name} programme. Congratulations!
                                                            </p>
                                                            <p>
                                                                The proposal had an average rating of <strong
                                                                >${object.rating_avg}</strong> with scale of 1-5.
                                                            </p>
                                                            <br />
